Package: zentyal-ntp
Architecture: all
Depends: zentyal-core (>= 7.1.0), zentyal-core (<< 7.2.0), zentyal-firewall,
         ntp, ntpdate, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Zentyal - NTP Service
 Zentyal is a Linux small business server that can act as
 a Gateway, Unified Threat Manager, Office Server, Infrastructure
 Manager, Unified Communications Server or a combination of them. One
 single, easy-to-use platform to manage all your network services.
 .
 This module adds a NTP server to Zentyal, allowing time synchronization from
 external servers and to internal clients.
